            <div class="col-md-9 text-left bottom-pad-20">
                <!-- Text -->
                <blockquote><em><p>GTH is your introduction to trade in Ghana, hosted by the Customs Division of Ghana Revenue Authority. Ghana's Trading hub is a one stop entry point and reliable tool used in providing quick access to an accurate real time trade Information. The portal provides comprehensive information on all necessary documentations licensed Permit Certificate and Others, fees that need to be paid, estimated processing time and other relevant information needed for an import or export transactions by the trading communities. </p>
<p>The Ghana's Trading Hub (GTH) is indeed a step in the right direction for  everyone who has an intent  to import or export as the information accessed  would  serve as a business guide to make you more informed and compliant with all trade related requirements and regulation eliminating  conflicting  guidelines  to  equip you  in making decision about doing business in Ghana.</p>
<p>The Ghana's Trading Hub is proudly owned by the Customs Division of Ghana Revenue Authority. The concept was initiated as part of its modernization efforts to facilitate trade, increase transparency and make trade easy in Ghana.</p>
<p>We hope you find the portal Informative, useful and enlightening.  Kindly visit the portal as often as you can and please do not hesitate to contact our help line or send in your enquiry for further clarifications</p>

<p style="text-align:right">Thank you</p></em></blockquote>
            </div>
